---

<Layout 
    title={title} 
    description={description}
    canonicalURL="https://huntertech.ca/services/managed-it-support/"
    keywords={keywords}
    type="website"
    image={itSupport.src}
    structuredData={structuredData}
>
    <Header />
    <main class="service-page">
        <Hero 
            title="Managed IT Support"
            subtitle="Proactive IT management and support for your business"
            backgroundImage={itSupport.src}
            backgroundImageAlt="IT support professional helping with computer issues"
            ctaText="Get started with managed IT services"
            ctaLink="/contact/?form_conversion=managed-it-support-hero-cta"
        />

        <section class="intro">
            <div class="managed-it-container">
                <div class="content">
                    <p>Technology is undeniably the backbone of modern businesses, driving efficiency, innovation, and growth. As businesses grow more reliant on digital infrastructure, IT responsibilities have become increasingly demanding, requiring constant vigilance, advanced skills, and rapid adaptation to new technologies and cybersecurity threats.</p>
                    <p>Huntertech is here to help. We offer expert support, proactive maintenance, and scalable solutions, ensuring smooth and secure operations for your daily business needs. Our <a href="/calgary/">managed IT services Calgary</a> and <a href="/vancouver/">managed IT services Vancouver</a> teams provide local expertise with comprehensive technology solutions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="why-us">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Why Huntertech?</h2>
                <div class="benefits-grid">
                    <div class="benefit-card">
